### 9.1 Module Docstrings

New modules require top-level docstring after banner:

```python
"""Long-term memory persistence for Titan user and project knowledge."""
```

### 9.2 Class Docstrings

Managers and agents document responsibility in one paragraph.

### 9.3 Method Docstrings

Public methods on managers require docstrings with:

