Update when changing system behavior:

- `Titan_Blueprint.md` — product milestones
- `core/constitution/titan_constitution.md` — identity/values (product team)
- This rulebook — engineering standards

Do not create random markdown files unless user requests or milestone requires.

### 9.5 Inline TODO Format

```python
